  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the ultimate physics-based football game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173530/extras/957f0f2f50467f2384efaf801b9b5487.poster.avif?t=1735781760\" width=554 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173530/extras/957f0f2f50467f2384efaf801b9b5487.webm?t=1735781760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173530/extras/957f0f2f50467f2384efaf801b9b5487.mp4?t=1735781760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Up to 10 players in the same match<br></li><li> Select multiple players in the pitch or only select your own<br></li><li> Customize your player/s<br></li><li> Play with friends or against friends<br></li><li> Play on a LAN match like the old days!<br></li><li> Invite your friends over Steam or join any Steam match available on the world<br></li><li> Master the Locoso's Spinning to become better at shooting and goalkeeping</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173530/extras/4e2e45888359e613f81277b2aa683f2a.poster.avif?t=1735781760\" width=554 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173530/extras/4e2e45888359e613f81277b2aa683f2a.webm?t=1735781760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173530/extras/4e2e45888359e613f81277b2aa683f2a.mp4?t=1735781760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
